17. The Desert Bloom (Agave & Pear)
Origin: Death & Co
Profile: Floral, Clean, Crisp, Subtly Smoky.
Inspired by a 50/50 Martini, this drink pairs agave flavors with pear. The "Master" version uses Pickle Brine to simulate the salinity of Manzanilla sherry.
The Architecture:
Seedlip Spice 94: Provides the allspice/cardamom base.
Pear Juice: Fresh pressed and filtered (passed through a coffee filter) to ensure clarity.
Component
Quantity
Notes
Seedlip Spice 94
1.5 oz (45ml)
Aromatic base.
Fresh Pear Juice
1 oz (30ml)
Sweet/Floral.
Verjus Blanc
0.5 oz (15ml)
Acid.
Agave Syrup
0.25 oz (7ml)
Sweetener.
Pickle Brine
Splash
The savory "sherry" note.

The Master Preparation:
Stir over ice and strain into a Nick & Nora glass. Garnish with a pear fan. The pickle brine is imperceptible as a distinct flavor but adds a savory depth that grounds the pear sweetness.
